bject-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.walk-ons.com/\">Walk-Ons Bistreaux &amp; Bar</a> celebrated their San Antonio grand opening the weekend of July 15th.  The restaurant was overflowing with excited VIP party guests, news groups, and restaurant staff and executives.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nSee what local news station, <a href=\"http://www.news4sa.com\">News 4 San Antonio</a>, had to say about new <a href=\"http://news4sanantonio.com/sa-living/food/drew-brees-now-has-a-san-antonio-connection\">New Orleans Saints quarterback Drew Brees new connection to San Antonio.</a><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\"><u>About The PM Group</u></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 30 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <em>San Antonio Business Journal</em>. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala every February that to date has raised over $2.5 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years!  It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"Walk-Ons Bistreaux & Bar Celebrates San Antonio Grand Opening","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Walk-Ons Bistreaux &amp; Bar Celebrates San Antonio Grand Opening","url":"/walk-ons-bistreaux-bar-celebrate-grand-opening/"}],"title":"Walk-Ons Bistreaux & Bar Celebrate San Antonio Grand Opening","metaDesc":"Walk-Ons Bistreaux & Bar celebrated their San Antonio grand opening the weekend of July 15th. The restaurant was overflowing with excited VIP party guests...","focuskw":"Walk-Ons","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"Walk-Ons Bistreaux & Bar Celebrate San Antonio 